#1 # 2024.06.24 # &ldquo;Prometheus stole fire from the gods and gave it to man&rdquo;
&ldquo;For this he was chained to a rock and torture d for eternity&rdquo;
​
&ldquo;프로메테우스는 신들의 불을 훔쳤다, 그리고 그것을 인간에게 주었다&rdquo;
&ldquo;그 죄로 그는 바위에 쇠사슬로 묶인 채 영원히 고문을 당해야 했다&rdquo;
​
FISSION Dr. Oppenheimer. As we begin, I believe you have a statement to read into the record. / Yes, Your Honor.
